Enum Class HttpStatus

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<HttpStatus>
io.micronaut.http.HttpStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, CharSequence, Comparable<HttpStatus>, Constable
public enum HttpStatus extends Enum<HttpStatus> implements CharSequence
Represents HTTP status codes. See https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec10.html.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Graeme Rocher
